<i>(doorbell rings)</i>

48:54.843 --> 48:56.342
<i>(TV playing in background)</i>

48:56.344 --> 48:58.811
<i>STEFANIA: Oh. Oh-oh-oh.</i>

48:58.813 --> 49:01.747
<i>(laughs)</i>

49:01.749 --> 49:03.982
<i>Oh. (laughs)</i>

49:03.984 --> 49:05.784
<i>What a nice surprise.</i>

49:05.786 --> 49:06.985
<i>PATRICK: After you called,</i>

49:06.987 --> 49:08.453
<i>I thought, it's been too long.</i>

49:08.455 --> 49:09.520
<i>STEFANIA: Ah, yes.</i>

49:09.522 --> 49:13.590
<i>PATRICK: I had some business in town, so
I thought I'd stop by and say hello.</i>

49:13.592 --> 49:15.859
<i>STEFANIA: Come, come, sit.</i>

49:15.861 --> 49:19.763
<i>I have some pastries I get for you.</i>

49:19.765 --> 49:23.333
<i>PATRICK: So, uh, how are
things at the church?</i>

49:23.335 --> 49:25.602
<i>You still involved like you used to be?</i>

49:25.604 --> 49:26.770
<i>STEFANIA: No.</i>

49:26.772 --> 49:29.673
<i>The new Monsignor is asshole.</i>

49:29.675 --> 49:33.743
<i>I left Ellen Parsons' card on the table.</i>

49:33.745 --> 49:36.713
<i>PATRICK: Thank you for
this, Mrs. McKee.</i>

49:36.715 --> 49:38.781
<i>STEFANIA: Of course.</i>

49:40.751 --> 49:44.520
<i>You help me, I help you.</i>

49:44.522 --> 49:47.589
<i>WILLIAMS: We got a DNA match.</i>

49:47.591 --> 49:48.857
<i>PARSONS: You get a hit?</i>

49:48.859 --> 49:50.993
<i>ORTIZ: Yeah, this knucklehead's
pulled a lot of</i>

49:50.995 --> 49:52.594
<i>crap, but it's all low-rent.</i>

49:52.596 --> 49:53.595
<i>Mostly theft.</i>

49:53.597 --> 49:55.898
<i>WILLIAMS: His name's
Patrick Scully.</i>

49:55.900 --> 49:58.800
<i>ORTIZ: Attempted murder seems
way out of his league.</i>

49:58.802 --> 50:00.869
<i>WILLIAMS: We checked his
last known address.</i>

50:00.871 --> 50:03.038
<i>It seems he left town several years ago.</i>

50:03.040 --> 50:04.106
<i>PARSONS: And?</i>

50:04.108 --> 50:06.308
<i>WILLIAMS: Well, apparently,
