50:08.378 --> 50:10.545
<i>WILLIAMS: Well, we put out a
bulletin; if he pops up</i>

50:10.547 --> 50:12.547
<i>anywhere, we'll let you know.</i>

50:12.549 --> 50:15.549
<i>I'm sorry, Miss Parsons, that's
about the best we can do.</i>

50:15.551 --> 50:17.584
<i>PARSONS: I understand.</i>

50:17.586 --> 50:19.986
<i>Thanks for your help.</i>

50:19.988 --> 50:22.055
<i>WILLIAMS: Sure.</i>

50:26.394 --> 50:29.128
