<i>FRANKLIN: Hey.</i>

50:45.648 --> 50:47.315
<i>I heard from Michael.</i>

50:47.317 --> 50:50.518
<i>Patty turned him down, I'm afraid.</i>

50:50.520 --> 50:52.387
<i>You look tired.</i>

50:52.389 --> 50:54.089
<i>That trip wiped you out.</i>

50:54.091 --> 50:55.290
<i>You need to sleep.</i>

50:55.292 --> 50:59.194
