52:04.760 --> 52:07.060
<i>Can you step out of the room, ma'am?</i>

52:07.062 --> 52:08.261
<i>Please, step out of the room.</i>

52:08.263 --> 52:10.163
<i>FRANKLIN: Okay, um,
uh, he has a DNR.</i>

52:10.165 --> 52:11.164
<i>Yes, we know.</i>

52:11.166 --> 52:12.165
<i>Who are you?</i>

52:12.167 --> 52:14.567
<i>FRANKLIN: Uh, I'm Kate
Franklin; I'm his daughter.</i>

52:14.569 --> 52:16.636
<i>(ripping noise)</i>

